    85вҶ’## API
    87вҶ’### ky(input, options?)
    89вҶ’The `input` and `options` are the same as [`fetch`](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/WindowOrWorkerGlobalScope/fetch), with additional `options` available (see below).
