  1050вҶ’## Tips
  1052вҶ’### Sending form data
  1054вҶ’Sending form data in Ky is identical to `fetch`. Just pass a [`FormData`](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData) instance to the `body` option. The `Content-Type` header will be automatically set to `multipart/form-data`, overriding any existing `Content-Type` header.
  1055вҶ’
      вҶ’вҖҰ
  1158вҶ’#### Native proxy support
  1160вҶ’Node.js 24.5+ supports automatic proxy configuration via environment variables. Set `NODE_USE_ENV_PROXY=1` or use the `--use-env-proxy` CLI flag.
  1161вҶ’
  1162вҶ’```sh
  1163вҶ’NODE_USE_ENV_PROXY=1 HTTP_PROXY=http://proxy.example.com:8080 node app.js
  1164вҶ’```
  1165вҶ’
  1166вҶ’Or:
  1167вҶ’
  1168вҶ’```sh
  1169вҶ’node --use-env-proxy app.js
  1170вҶ’```
  1171вҶ’
  1172вҶ’Supported environment variables:
